resources.name: Invite Clinical Rater
resources.description:
This endpoint invites clinical raters to clinical tests.
The only required field in the data request is the user's email.
If the user exists in the database, he will be assigned to test automatically. 
If not, the system will send an invite email.

The request is like this:
~~~json
{
	"email": "dummy@tavos.com"
}
~~~

When user found in databse the response will be like this:

~~~json
{
	"Notice": "We found a user. We sent an email to notify him."
}
~~~

If not, the return is like this:

~~~json
{
	"Notice": "User not found. We sent an invite email inviting him to join in the clinical test."
}
~~~
